content:
InsPolicyBillingService Methods

These are the available methods:

InsPolicyBillingService:generateBillingAccountStatements
Use this service to generate statements for accounts with policies that have billing accounts due today.

InsPolicyBillingService:generateDirectBillingStatements
Use this service to generate statements for accounts containing policies with direct billing whose due date is 10 days from today.
title: InsPolicyBillingService Methods and Usage
